.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/094-playbook-prompt-naturalness/plan.md:76:Doc-as-code refactor with template-driven generation. cli-codex applies the heuristic per scenario, updates two locations (SCENARIO CONTRACT + 9-col table cell) to maintain prompt-equality, and reports per-playbook conversion counts.
