.opencode/skills/sk-code-review/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:48:This playbook provides 18 deterministic scenarios across 6 categories validating the `sk-code-review` skill surface and its review-agent consumers. Each scenario maps to a dedicated per-feature file with exact prompt, command sequence, expected signals, evidence, pass/fail criteria, and failure triage.
.opencode/skills/sk-code-review/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:56:3. The operator captures the exact prompt, command transcript, evidence files, and final review handback.
