.opencode/skills/sk-code-review/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:415:Prompt: `Run a security-only review on the requested diff scope, suppressing style-only advice while keeping security-impact correctness blockers.`
.opencode/skills/sk-code-review/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:431:Prompt: `Review this diff against detected sk-code surface evidence, letting surface conventions win while baseline security and correctness still block.`
.opencode/skills/sk-code-review/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:447:Prompt: `Review the staged test-only diff for assertion-free tests, swallowed assertions, over-mocking, flaky state, and cleanup gaps.`
.opencode/skills/sk-code-review/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:469:Prompt: `Re-review this follow-up diff against the original findings, closing each P0/P1 with current evidence or leaving it open.`
