.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:755:Prompt: `Validate startup runtime compatibility guards and confirm the targeted diagnostics suite covers runtime mismatch, marker creation, and SQLite diagnostics.`
