.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:789:Prompt: `Validate chunk collapse deduplication (G3) for memory_search(includeContent:false) and confirm collapsed chunks return unique parent IDs.`
.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/manual_testing_playbook/manual_testing_playbook.md:803:Prompt: `Validate co-activation fan-effect divisor (R17) and confirm hub scores dampen by fan-out without changing non-hub scores.`
