.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/096-rename-opencode-dirs-to-plural/spec.md:86: - Fixing the 19 pre-existing broken `.gemini/workflows/*` symlinks (point to wrong absolute path "Opencode Env"; pre-dates this packet).
